# Features Log

This file tracks nodes and features added by the automated OpenCode agent.

## Format

Each entry should follow this format:
```
## YYYY-MM-DD - Feature/Node Name
- Model ID: `provider/model-name`
- Category: `image`, `video`, or `audio`
- Description: Brief summary of what was added
```

---

## 2026-01-15 - Kie Model Sync (No New Models Found)

Comprehensive scan of Kie.ai marketplace and API documentation revealed that nearly all documented models are already implemented in the codebase:

- **Image nodes**: Flux 2 Pro/Flex, Seedream 4.5, Z-Image Turbo, Nano Banana/Pro, Flux Kontext, Grok Imagine, Qwen, Topaz Upscaler, Recraft, Ideogram
- **Video nodes**: Kling 2.5/2.6, Kling AI Avatar, Grok Imagine Video, Seedance V1, Hailuo 2.3, Sora 2, Wan 2.1/2.6, Topaz Video Upscale, Infinitalk
- **Audio nodes**: Suno Music Generator

No new models were added in this sync cycle.
